OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather grey start in places
OL,6,Fbut cloud will lift and break allowing
OL,7,Fsome good spells of sunshine to
OL,8,Fdevelop. A few showers also possible
OL,9,Fbut many will remain dry. Feeling
OL,10,Ffresher than of late.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry evening with some late
OL,13,Fspells of sunshine. Overnight cloud
OL,14,Fwill gradually spread in from the west
OL,15,Fbut remaining dry throughout. Mild.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FSome early brightness
OL,18,Fpossible, otherwise a grey day on
OL,19,FMonday with a band of rain gradually
OL,20,Fmoving eastwards. The rain heavy at
OL,21,Ftimes, especially during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
