OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FRather
OL,6,Fchangeable throughout the period with
OL,7,Fa mix of sunshine and showers
OL,8,Finterspersed with a longer spell of
OL,9,Frain on Wednesday. Temperatures near
OL,10,Faverage for early June.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
